  "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>Serenity 紫苏叶逆向投研日报 — 2026年7月6日</title>\n<style>\n  :root {\n    --bg: #0d1117;\n    --card: #161b22;\n    --border: #30363d;\n    --text: #e6edf3;\n    --muted: #8b949e;\n    --accent: #f0883e;\n    --green: #3fb950;\n    --red: #f85149;\n    --blue: #58a6ff;\n    --purple: #bc8cff;\n    --yellow: #d29922;\n    --pink: #f778ba;\n  }\n  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n  body {\n    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Noto Sans CJK SC', sans-serif;\n    background: var(--bg);\n    color: var(--text);\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    padding: 20px;\n    max-width: 1200px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n  .header {\n    text-align: center;\n    padding: 40px 0 30px;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n    margin-bottom: 30px;\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(240,136,62,0.1), rgba(188,140,255,0.1));\n    border-radius: 16px;\n  }\n  .header h1 {\n    font-size: 28px;\n    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--purple));\n    -webkit-background-clip: text;\n    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n  .header .subtitle {\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 14px;\n  }\n  .header .meta {\n    margin-top: 12px;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n    gap: 24px;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n  }\n  .header .meta span {\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);\n    padding: 4px 14px;\n    border-radius: 20px;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    color: var(--muted);\n  }\n  .section {\n    background: var(--card);\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    padding: 28px;\n    margin-bottom: 24px;\n  }\n  .section-title {\n    font-size: 20px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    padding-bottom: 12px;\n    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 10px;\n  }\n  .section-title .icon {\n    width: 32px; height: 32px;\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\n    font-size: 16px;\n  }\n  .icon-fire { background: rgba(248,81,73,0.2); }\n  .icon-doc { background: rgba(88,166,255,0.2); }\n  .icon-filter { background: rgba(188,140,255,0.2); }\n  .icon-chart { background: rgba(63,185,80,0.2); }\n  .icon-strategy { background: rgba(240,136,62,0.2); }\n  .icon-review { background: rgba(210,153,34,0.2); }\n\n  .market-index-row {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));\n    gap: 16px;\n    margin-bottom: 24px;\n  }\n  .idx-card {\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    padding: 16px;\n    text-align: center;\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n  }\n  .idx-card .name { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); }\n  .idx-card .val { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin: 4px 0; }\n  .idx-card .chg { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; }\n  .up { color: var(--green); }\n  .down { color: var(--red); }\n\n  .hot-boards {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));\n    gap: 16px;\n    margin-top: 16px;\n  }\n  .board-card {\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    padding: 18px;\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n  }\n  .board-card h4 {\n    font-size: 15px;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 8px;\n  }\n  .board-card ul { list-style: none; }\n  .board-card li {\n    font-size: 13px;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    padding: 3px 0;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);\n  }\n  .board-card li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n  .board-card li strong { color: var(--text); }\n  .tag {\n    display: inline-block;\n    padding: 2px 8px;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    font-size: 11px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n  .tag-hot { background: rgba(248,81,73,0.2); color: var(--red); }\n  .tag-policy { background: rgba(88,166,255,0.2); color: var(--blue); }\n  .tag-money { background: rgba(63,185,80,0.2); color: var(--green); }\n  .tag-event { background: rgba(188,140,255,0.2); color: var(--purple); }\n\n  table {\n    width: 100%;\n    border-collapse: collapse;\n    font-size: 14px;\n  }\n  th {\n    text-align: left;\n    padding: 10px 12px;\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\n    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);\n    font-weight: 600;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    white-space: nowrap;\n  }\n  td {\n    padding: 10px 12px;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);\n    vertical-align: middle;\n  }\n  tr:hover td { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }\n  .stock-name { font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }\n  .stock-code { color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; }\n  .score-badge {\n    display: inline-block;\n    padding: 3px 10px;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    font-size: 14px;\n  }\n  .score-high { background: rgba(63,185,80,0.2); color: var(--green); }\n  .score-mid { background: rgba(240,136,62,0.2); color: var(--accent); }\n  .score-low { background: rgba(248,81,73,0.2); color: var(--red); }\n  .rating-tag {\n    display: inline-block;\n    padding: 2px 10px;\n    border-radius: 4px;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n  .rating-buy { background: rgba(63,185,80,0.15); color: var(--green); }\n  .rating-watch { background: rgba(210,153,34,0.15); color: var(--yellow); }\n  .rating-sell { background: rgba(248,81,73,0.15); color: var(--red); }\n  .rating-hold { background: rgba(88,166,255,0.15); color: var(--blue); }\n\n  .triangle-viz {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 20px;\n    margin: 20px 0;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n  }\n  .tri-col {\n    flex: 1;\n    min-width: 200px;\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    padding: 16px;\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n  }\n  .tri-col h5 { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 14px; }\n  .bar-group { margin: 8px 0; }\n  .bar-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 3px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; }\n  .bar-track { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 4px; height: 8px; overflow: hidden; }\n  .bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; transition: width 0.5s; }\n  .bar-green { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #238636, var(--green)); }\n  .bar-blue { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1f6feb, var(--blue)); }\n  .bar-purple { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #8b5cf6, var(--purple)); }\n\n  .strategy-cards {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(340px, 1fr));\n    gap: 16px;\n  }\n  .strat-card {\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    padding: 20px;\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  .strat-card .rank {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: -1px; left: -1px;\n    background: var(--accent);\n    color: #fff;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    padding: 3px 10px;\n    border-radius: 10px 0 10px 0;\n  }\n  .strat-card h4 { font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 4px; padding-top: 4px; }\n  .strat-card .track { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 12px; }\n  .strat-card .detail { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin: 6px 0; }\n  .strat-card .detail strong { color: var(--text); }\n  .strat-card .action-box {\n    background: rgba(63,185,80,0.08);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(63,185,80,0.2);\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    padding: 12px;\n    margin-top: 12px;\n    font-size: 13px;\n  }\n  .strat-card .action-box.warn {\n    background: rgba(210,153,34,0.08);\n    border-color: rgba(210,153,34,0.2);\n  }\n  .strat-card .action-box.danger {\n    background: rgba(248,81,73,0.08);\n    border-color: rgba(248,81,73,0.2);\n  }\n\n  .review-summary {\n    background: rgba(210,153,34,0.06);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(210,153,34,0.15);\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    padding: 16px;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    font-size: 14px;\n  }\n  .review-summary h4 { color: var(--yellow); margin-bottom: 8px; }\n\n  .perf-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n    gap: 16px;\n    margin-top: 16px;\n  }\n  .perf-card {\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    padding: 16px;\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n  }\n  .perf-card h5 { font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; }\n  .perf-card .metric {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    padding: 4px 0;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);\n    font-size: 13px;\n  }\n  .perf-card .metric:last-child { border-bottom: none; }\n\n  .policy-list {\n    list-style: none;\n    counter-reset: policy;\n  }\n  .policy-list li {\n    counter-increment: policy;\n    padding: 12px 0 12px 40px;\n    position: relative;\n    border-left: 2px solid var(--border);\n    margin-left: 14px;\n    font-size: 14px;\n  }\n  .policy-list li::before {\n    content: counter(policy);\n    position: absolute;\n    left: -11px;\n    top: 14px;\n    width: 20px; height: 20px;\n    background: var(--accent);\n    color: #fff;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    font-size: 11px;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    font-weight: 700;\n  }\n  .policy-list li strong { color: var(--blue); }\n\n  .disclaimer {\n    background: rgba(248,81,73,0.06);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(248,81,73,0.15);\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    padding: 20px;\n    margin-top: 30px;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    line-height: 1.8;\n  }\n  .disclaimer h4 {\n    color: var(--red);\n    font-size: 14px;\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n\n  .highlight-box {\n    background: rgba(240,136,62,0.08);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(240,136,62,0.2);\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    padding: 16px;\n    margin: 16px 0;\n    font-size: 14px;\n  }\n  .highlight-box strong { color: var(--accent); }\n\n  .highlight-box.green {\n    background: rgba(63,185,80,0.08);\n    border-color: rgba(63,185,80,0.2);\n  }\n  .highlight-box.green strong { color: var(--green); }\n\n  .highlight-box.red {\n    background: rgba(248,81,73,0.08);\n    border-color: rgba(248,81,73,0.2);\n  }\n  .highlight-box.red strong { color: var(--red); }\n\n  .funds-flow {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n    gap: 12px;\n    margin-top: 12px;\n  }\n  .fund-item {\n    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    padding: 12px;\n    text-align: center;\n    border: 1px solid var(--border);\n  }\n  .fund-item .label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); }\n  .fund-item .value { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 4px; }\n\n  .note { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 12px; font-style: italic; }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<div class=\"header\">\n  <h1>Serenity 紫苏叶逆向投研日报</h1>\n  <div class=\"subtitle\">2026年7月6日（周一） | 万亿逆回购落地 · 新规施行 · 机器人+黄金双主线延续</div>\n  <div class=\"meta\">\n    <span>紫苏叶理论 v3.0</span>\n    <span>逆向投研框架</span>\n    <span>数据截止：2026-07-03 收盘（周末休市）</span>\n    <span>第10期</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- ===================== SECTION 1: 市场热点概览 ===================== -->\n<div class=\"section\">\n  <div class=\"section-title\">\n    <span class=\"icon icon-fire\">🔥</span> 市场热点概览\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"market-index-row\">\n    <div class=\"idx-card\">\n      <div class=\"name\">上证指数</div>\n      <div class=\"val\">4,043.64</div>\n      <div class=\"chg up\">+0.37%</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"idx-card\">\n      <div class=\"name\">深证成指</div>\n      <div class=\"val\">15,597.51</div>\n      <div class=\"chg up\">+0.64%</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"idx-card\">\n      <div class=\"name\">创业板指</div>\n      <div class=\"val\">4,019.93</div>\n      <div class=\"chg up\">+0.07%</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"idx-card\">\n      <div class=\"name\">科创50</div>\n      <div class=\"val\">1,975.60</div>\n      <div class=\"chg down\">-0.59%</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"idx-card\">\n      <div class=\"name\">北证50</div>\n      <div class=\"val\">—</div>\n      <div class=\"chg up\">+1.71%</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"highlight-box green\">\n    <strong>核心结论：</strong>7月3日（上周五）三大指数集体反弹但冲高回落，上证收涨0.37%至4043点，创业板仅微涨0.07%。市场成交缩量至约3.18-3.21万亿元（较前日缩量2680亿元），表明增量资金观望情绪浓。周末央行1万亿买断式逆回购落地+A股交易新规正式施行，7月6日（周一）开盘面临两大事件催化剂。核心主线不变：人形机器人（40余只涨停，板块+9.12%）、贵金属（非农爆冷驱动）、军工（地缘催化），而半导体/算力硬件持续遭遇资金流出。\n  </div>\n\n  <h4 style=\"margin: 20px 0 12px; font-size: 15px;\">🔥 主线热点与板块分布（7月3日收盘）</h4>\n  <div class=\"hot-boards\">\n    <div class=\"board-card\">\n      <h4><span class=\"tag tag-hot\">主线</span> 人形机器人/具身智能（最强）</h4>\n      <ul>\n        <li>板块指数单日涨 <strong>+9.12%</strong>，<strong>40余只</strong>成分股涨停</li>\n        <li>宇树科技科创板IPO注册获批（7/2），募资约 <strong>42亿元</strong></li>\n        <li>埃斯顿4天3板、绿的谐波收涨超18%</li>\n        <li>主力净流入 <strong>+39.15亿</strong></li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"board-card\">\n      <h4><span class=\"tag tag-hot\">主线</span> 贵金属/黄金（非农催化）</h4>\n      <ul>\n        <li>美国6月非农仅5.7万人，远低于预期11万</li>\n        <li>现货黄金涨 <strong>+2.41%</strong> 至 <strong>4132美元/盎司</strong></li>\n        <li>赤峰黄金、山金国际高开超6%，招金黄金、四川黄金涨停</li>\n        <li>板块净流入 <strong>+32.6亿</strong></li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"board-card\">\n      <h4><span class=\"tag tag-policy\">政策</span> 军工（地缘+订单）</h4>\n      <ul>\n        <li>军工指数 <strong>+3.19%</strong>、中证军工 <strong>+3.44%</strong></li>\n        <li>光电股份、中航沈飞等领涨</li>\n        <li>催化：地缘政治紧张+中报订单预期</li>\n        <li>军工电子/信息化方向领涨</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"board-card\">\n      <h4><span class=\"tag tag-money\">资金</span> 汽车零部件（共振）</h4>\n      <ul>\n        <li><strong>21只</strong>个股涨停</li>\n        <li>三花智控净流入 <strong>21.88亿</strong></li>\n        <li>新能源车补贴政策+出海逻辑+机器人产业链共振</li>\n        <li>板块主力净流入 <strong>+68.93亿</strong>（全市场第一）</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"board-card\">\n      <h4><span class=\"tag tag-event\">事件</span> 有色金属（供需收紧）</h4>\n      <ul>\n        <li>沪铜库存降至年内新低</li>\n        <li>LME铜单周去库 <strong>4.4%</strong></li>\n        <li>板块主力净流入 <strong>+49.69亿</strong></li>\n        <li>供需双端共振，铜/铝/锌全面走强</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"board-card\">\n      <h4><span class=\"tag tag-policy\">政策</span> 医药/创新药</h4>\n      <ul>\n        <li>中证医药 <strong>+2.04%</strong></li>\n        <li>医保谈判边际缓和+估值历史低位+机构低配回补</li>\n        <li>海南海药延续强势</li>\n        <li>政策底确认，关注中报业绩催化</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <h4 style=\"margin: 24px 0 12px; font-size: 15px;\">⚠️ 资金出逃板块（7月3日）</h4>\n  <table>\n    <tr>\n      <th>板块</th>\n      <th>7/3净流出</th>\n      <th>核心出逃标的</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>半导体/存储芯片</td>\n      <td class=\"down\">-92.6亿</td>\n      <td>京东方A(-51.58亿)、兆易创新(-30.61亿)</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>光通信/算力硬件</td>\n      <td class=\"down\">-47.3亿</td>\n      <td>亨通光电(-10.63亿)</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>氟化工/新材料</td>\n      <td class=\"down\">-28.1亿</td>\n      <td>前期氟化工涨价潮后回调</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>传媒互联网</td>\n      <td class=\"down\">-16.8亿</td>\n      <td>AI应用缺乏新增催化</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>光伏硅片</td>\n      <td class=\"down\">-12.4亿</td>\n      <td>产能过剩担忧持续</td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n\n  <div class=\"funds-flow\">\n    <div class=\"fund-item\">\n      <div class=\"label\">7/3主力净流出</div>\n      <div class=\"value down\">-175.91亿</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"fund-item\">\n      <div class=\"label\">北向资金（近7日）</div>\n      <div class=\"value down\">-82.6亿（海外算力）</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"fund-item\">\n      <div class=\"label\">北向加仓（近7日）</div>\n      <div class=\"value up\">+114.3亿（国产半导体）</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"fund-item\">\n      <div class=\"label\">两市成交额</div>\n      <div class=\"value\">3.18万亿</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  